Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.77,0:00:17.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いまだ何も知らず　何者でもない王子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.83,0:00:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Inconspicuous prince who has nothing does not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:21.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし　彼は後に王と呼ばれることになる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.82,0:00:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But in due time, he will become king.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:25.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,その者の名は　アルスラーン
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And his name Arslan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter last
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The era of pars, 320 a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:35.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルス暦３２０年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.17,0:00:41.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルスの豊かな領土を狙い　異教徒の国　ルシタニアが侵攻を開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Lyusitaniya, following a belief,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,launched an invasion to capture a prosperous Pars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.52,0:00:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Maru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.52,0:00:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Atropatene
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.52,0:00:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Parsee
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.85,0:00:48.37,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルス王　アンドラゴラス三世は自ら軍を率い　ルシタニアを迎え撃つ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,King Parsis, Andragoras III of,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,personally I led an army against Lyusitanii.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.14,0:00:51.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王太子アルスラーン　初陣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Arslan came to the battle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.19,0:00:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The heir to the throne of the kingdom of Pars, Arslan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:53.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,時に１４歳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in fourteen years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:59.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,圧倒的に有利と思われたアトロパテネにおける大戦は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Battle of Atropatena
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:00:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It was supposed to end in their favor,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.42,0:01:04.28,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,カーラーンの裏切りにより　累々たるパルス軍の屍を積み重ねた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.51,0:01:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but, because of the treachery of Harlan,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.45,0:01:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,completed countless casualties among the soldiers Parsis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.31,0:01:08.11,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,華々しく飾られるはずであった初陣は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The first fight, which was supposed to be amazing,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It turned into a living hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:10.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,さながら地獄となった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Traitor, captain of cavalry, Harlan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:17.57,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,カーラーン　なぜだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.75,0:01:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Harlan, why ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.11,0:01:19.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,故あってのことです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.21,0:01:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So there were circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.28,0:01:22.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,悲しく　あわれな王子よ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The poor and the wretched Prince,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:24.37,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,敵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.47,0:01:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.51,0:01:27.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.58,0:01:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.11,0:01:29.27,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.28,0:01:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Darjun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain of Cavalry of the kingdom Pars, Daryun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to save you, Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.77,0:01:42.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,今　お助けいたします　殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:45.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,しばしそこでお待ちください
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.68,0:01:48.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,このダリューンがお守りいたしますゆえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.70,0:01:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I Daryun, will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I rely on you, Daryun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:52.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,後は任せた　ダリューン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.85,0:01:54.91,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,待て　ダリューン　話を聞け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Daryun! Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.91,0:01:56.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,今更　何を言う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.14,0:01:59.77,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,国王陛下を裏切り　王太子殿下にこのようなまねを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.15,0:01:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Betraying His Majesty the King
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:01:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Crown Prince, do you dare ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! If you know the reason you will not even blame ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:02.89,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,待て　事情を知れば　お主とて　俺の行為を責めは…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:10.77,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ここは一旦退くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:12.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,カーラーン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Harlan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:22.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,同日　夕刻を前にして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.88,0:02:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,On the same day, when dusk fell back,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.82,0:02:28.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,無敗を誇ったアンドラゴラス三世率いるパルス軍は　大敗を喫した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.88,0:02:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,proud invincible army under the leadership of Parsis Andragorasa III
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He suffered a crushing defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Eighteenth kingdom pars ruler Andragoras III
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:32.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,蛮族どもめが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To these barbarians!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:37.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン　殿下をお守りいたせ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Daryun, Baby Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:40.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,General wage kingdom Lyusitaniya, Mr. Silver Mask
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:58.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,敗残の老いぼれが　出過ぎたまねをするな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeated a fool, do not stick your nose where you are powerless!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:10.28,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そやつを王などと呼ぶな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not call him king.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は何者だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:21.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,これほどの憎しみを受けながら　私が誰かも分からぬほど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You - the subject of fierce hatred,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but you do not even know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:23.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,悪行を重ねてきたか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.83,0:03:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How much evil you have done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sixteen years...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:27.57,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,１６年…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:32.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この日が来るのを１６年間待ち続けたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I waited for this day sixteen years,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:35.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アンドラゴラス
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.66,0:03:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Andragoras!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:42.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下　私の後ろを離れないでください
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince, please do not go very far from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Shabrang understands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:45.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だ　シャブラングが理解してくれている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My father stepped ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:55.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,父上は退却したのか　王都へ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In the capital?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:59.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,早く王都に戻らなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to get back to the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:03.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし　王都へ戻るには　このまま戦場を突っ切らねばなりません
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But to get back to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,we will have to cross the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:07.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,マルズバーンたちがこれほど倒されているということは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If so many people from marzban killed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,on the way to the capital city can be full of soldiers Lyusitanii.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:11.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王都までの道はルシタニア兵であふれ返っていると思われます
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:12.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:16.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,我が友　ナルサスを頼りましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlisted the help of my friend Narsusu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:26.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ナルサスとは　いつぞやのお主が言っていた　ひねくれ者の友か
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And this Narsus ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your wayward one, which was discussed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:29.57,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はい　元ダイラムの領主でございました
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Once he was the ruler of Daylama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:33.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いたことがある　父上によって宮廷を追放されたと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Father removed him from the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:38.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,数年前　三国同盟が我が国に侵入した折
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A few years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,When in our alliance invaded kingdoms troyh kingdoms
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:42.25,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,兵を一人も使わずに　敵軍を退散させた男です
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He shoved the enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,do not go into battle any soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He will meet with me, son of a king?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:46.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王の息子の私に会ってくれるだろうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:51.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そこはそれ　幸いというのも妙ですが　このありさま
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the country will call it luck,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but in our position ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:56.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ひねくれ者ゆえ　我々惨めな敗残者を拒みはしません
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him and wayward,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but he will not give up the conquered people, like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:59.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,惨めな敗残者…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The defeated people ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:07.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,今日のところはもうどうしようもございません
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we do not do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:12.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,後日　国王陛下と共に復讐戦を挑み　敵を討ちましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Later we together with His Majesty will surely find
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,way to get revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:18.97,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,今は生きてこそでございます
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,we need to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:28.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ナルサスは絵が好きなのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Narsus love to draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:34.28,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ…　誰にでも欠点はあるものでして
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We all have our weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:40.37,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの男は　天行の運行　異国の地理　暦史の変化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows about the movement of celestial bodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the geography of the land, the course of history ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:42.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんでも知らぬことはございません
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing he does not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:47.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ですが　たった一つ　自分の絵の技量についてだけは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only one ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,With regard to skills as an artist,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:49.57,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いわゆる　下手の横好き…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,it can be called a mountain enthusiast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Elam, is that you ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,エラムか　俺はダリューンだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It Daryun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:06:00.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お前のご主人に会いに来た　ここを通してもらえぬか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:05:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have come to see your master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Not propustysh us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:04.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,これは…　ダリューン様
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow ... Mr. Daryun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:07.25,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お久しぶりでございます
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How many years have passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Servant Narsusa, Elam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:10.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,知らぬこととはいえ　失礼をいたしました
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I do not know, but I'm sorry for being rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:19.91,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ナルサス　俺だ　ダリューンだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Narsus, it's me, Daryun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:32.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,名乗る必要はない　騒々しいヤツめ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Can not predstavlyatsya, screamer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Former governor Daylama, Narsus
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:38.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お主の声は１ファルサングも遠くから聞こえておったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I have long heard your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:43.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アトロパテネで我が軍は惨敗したのだな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Our army fell under Atropatena?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:46.77,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,カーラーンが裏切った
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Harlan betrayed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:48.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Daryun, thank you for the flattery,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:52.76,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかくだが　今更　浮世と縁を持つ気はない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but now I do not want to communicate with global issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:56.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし　山奥で下手な絵を描き散らしているより　はるかにましだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's better than be locked somewhere in the mountains with lousy pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:07:01.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この男を信用なさってはいけませんぞ　殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:07:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not trust this man, Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:05.98,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-1.5\fs51}こいつは「マルダーン・フ・マルダーン」で物の道理もよくわきまえておりますが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He Fu Mardan Mardan, also with a head on his shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:08.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,芸術を理解する心を持ちません
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just not quite able to appreciate art!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What art ?! You're ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:10.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何が芸術だ　お主のは…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:15.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,芸術は永遠　興亡は一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Art is eternal! Changes - are fleeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:46.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,エラム
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Elam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:49.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おはようございます　殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask one question?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:53.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,一つ聞かせてくれぬか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:57.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,エラムの両親は奴隷から解放されたのだったな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your parents were slaves, but they were released, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:58.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:07:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When the previous governor, Mr. Theos died,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:02.28,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,前領主テオス様がお亡くなりになり
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:05.77,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ナルサス様が相続なされたときのことです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Narsus became heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:09.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,全ての奴隷を解放してくださいました
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He then freed all the slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:11.91,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ならば　自由の身であろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're a free man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:14.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜいつまでもナルサスのもとにおるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why still sluzhysh Narsusu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:19.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私の意志でおそばにおります
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm staying with him on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:28.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,人は皆　平等だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All people are equal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:34.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり　奴隷は解放すべきなのだろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you need to free the slaves?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:40.91,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ご自分でお考えなさいませ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about this question for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.42,0:08:43.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私からも頼む
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also going to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me with Daryunom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:46.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューンと共に　私を助けてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:48.77,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがたいお言葉ですが…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for saying this, but ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:50.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,では　こうしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:56.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私はお主の忠誠を求める代わりに　十分な代償を支払う
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In return for your loyalty, I'll pay you handsomely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:09:01.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私がルシタニアを追い払い　パルスの国王になった暁には…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:09:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as we will repulse Lyusitanii, and I'm the king of Parsa ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:06.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ナルサス卿　お主を宮廷画家として迎えよう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Narsus, I will appoint you a painter in the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:08.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:17.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,気に入った
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:20.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,分かりました
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I Narsus,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:27.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,このナルサス　アルスラーン殿下にお仕えいたします
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I will serve you, Prince Arslan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:32.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう　ナルサス
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank Narsus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:36.11,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そうと決まれば　早々に出立しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Once everything has been decided, we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.28,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメだ　門が…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Useless! The gates! ..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Stands before the gates! Do not let anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:48.77,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,門の前で固めろ　侵入を許すな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:02.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルス暦３２０年１１月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The era of Pars, November 320 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:06.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王都エクバターナ　陥落
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The capital of Ecbatana fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:11.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,国王アンドラゴラスの生死も不明のまま
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.55,0:10:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The fate of King Andragorasa is still unknown,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:14.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルスは混乱の闇に落ちた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Pars and plunged into the darkness of chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:27.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-1\fs52}一方　アトロパテネでの敗戦の報を受けたミスラ神殿の神官　ファランギースは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, the terrible defeat at Atropatena
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned the priestess of the temple of Mithras, Farangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Rica temple Mitra, Farangis
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:32.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,旅の楽士　ギーブと共に　アルスラーン一行との合流を果たし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Together with a traveling musician Gievom
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wandering musician Giev
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,she joined a group of Arslan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to repulse the haunting of their general-perebezchiku Harlan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:37.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,一行を追う裏切りの将　カーラーンの軍勢を迎え撃つ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Atropatene
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Royal capital of Ecbatana
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We catch the traitor Harlan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:41.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,これから　裏切り者のカーラーンを捕らえて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:44.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルスラーン殿下のもとへ連れていく
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and move to the Prince Arslan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:47.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,人手が増えるのはありがたいことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Additional strength is to be welcomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:50.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,今　殿下にお仕えしているのは何人か
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people are currently prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:54.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,俺と俺のレータク　それに天下無双の騎士１人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My servant, I
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and one skilled knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:59.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そして　お主らを入れて　５人になった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And with you there will be only five.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.31,0:11:04.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,５人…ね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Five, right? ..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いたぞ　崖の上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,At the top of the cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.25,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,カーラーン
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Harlan, I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:11.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私なら　ここだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:18.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,これ以上　罪のない人を殺めること　見過ごすわけにはいかぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not stand by and watch you kill innocent people!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:21.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルスラーン
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Lions!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:26.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,カーラーン お主に尋ねたい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Harlan, I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.11,0:11:29.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,マルズバーンとして…　いや
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Marzʙana ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No. As the knight of the kingdom Pars ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:32.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それ以前から　パルスの騎士として
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.43,0:11:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody even behind your back bad word did not say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.48,0:11:35.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,誰にも後ろ指をさされたことがないお主が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.45,0:11:38.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ　ルシタニアなどに膝を屈したのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.49,0:11:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you bow to Lyusitaniey ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:41.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,欲に釣られたとも思えぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not believe you mastered greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:43.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,理由があるなら　ぜひ教えてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is a reason, tell it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:46.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,知らぬがお主のためだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You better not to know for your own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider me, Harlan, vile traitor, and die,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:52.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,このカーラーンを醜悪な裏切り者と信じて死んでいくがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:55.56,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アンドラゴラスの呪われた子よ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Andragorasa unfortunate son!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:11:59.78,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.91,0:12:03.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様の相手はこの俺だ　カーラーン
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your enemy, Harlan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:04.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Darjun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You punk! Know the location!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:21.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,青二才が　つけあがるな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:28.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,背中　取った
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:36.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,まだだ　まだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No! That's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:41.57,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,カーラーン
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Harlan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:47.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,カーラーン　王はどこにおられる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Harlan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the king ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:50.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800}王は…生きておる…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.81,0:12:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,King alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Royal capital of Ecbatana, dungeon
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Andragoras.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:00.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アンドラゴラスよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Eighteenth kingdom pars ruler Andragoras III
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:04.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が誰だか分かるか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:07.28,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,教えてやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:10.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,聞き覚えのない名ではないはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This name should be familiar to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:13.45,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の名はヒルメス
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I called Hermes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My father - Osroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:15.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,父はオスロエスだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:17.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ヒルメス
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hermes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Hermes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:20.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　ヒルメスだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:24.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,先王オスロエスの嫡子で　貴様の甥だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Heir Osroesa, the previous king, and your nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:28.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そして　パルスの真の国王だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,AND...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,True king Parsis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Royal capital of Ecbatana
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.15,0:13:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Atropatene
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:35.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王は生きている
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,King was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,After learning about it from Harlan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:38.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,カーラーンから新たな情報を得て
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Daryun Narsus and entered the royal capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:42.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューンとナルサスは王都へと潜入した
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that a man is looking for something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:54.45,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何事か　探っている者がいると聞いてな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:07.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン　教えてやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Daryun, I have something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:13.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様の伯父ヴァフリーズを殺ったのは　この俺だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your uncle was killed Vahriza me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.28,0:14:13.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:19.77,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アンドラゴラスの飼い犬めがそれにふさわしい報いを受けたわ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.63,0:14:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This dog Andragorasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He got what he deserved!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:22.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様の死にざまも伯父に倣うか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And you follow out his uncle ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And you follow out his uncle ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:43.07,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おのれ　ダリューン
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:44.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,やけど
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:05.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ここは一旦退いた方がよさそうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we better yet back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:06.59,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:14.11,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,エクバターナへの潜入を果たし
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Infiltrating in Ecbatana
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.62,0:15:18.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アンドラゴラス王とタハミーネ王妃の生存の感触を得た
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.62,0:15:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and knew that the king and queen Andragoras Tahameney probably alive
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:23.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ナルサスとダリューンは再びアルスラーン王子のもとへ戻った
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Narsus Daryun and again returned to Prince Arslan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Be that as it may, we have very few people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:28.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いずれにしても　我々は少数すぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.35,0:15:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we find allies?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.37,0:15:29.97,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,どうやって味方を増やせばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:32.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それには　殿下が将来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You, Prince, announced to the people Parsis,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:36.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,今までの国政において　条理に合わぬことをなくすと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that in the future you will be scattered all the chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:38.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルスの民にお示しになるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,who now reigned in the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,First, it specifies that wants to make a prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.57,0:15:43.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,まずは殿下の目指されるものを明らかになさいませ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And we will do our best to fulfill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:47.91,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それがかなうように　我らは努力させていただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:50.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルスラーンは王都を奪還するため
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,To return to the royal capital,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:54.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルスの最大戦力を残しているペシャワールを目指す
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.06,0:15:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Arslan went to Peshavard, which remained most of the Parsis forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:16:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Royal capital of Ecbatana
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:16:01.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-0.5}道中　追撃を振り払うため　カシャーン城塞へと身を寄せたアルスラーンは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Along the way, avoiding enemies chase
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.59,0:16:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Arslan had found refuge in the fortress of Kashan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:07.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,城塞の主　ホディーの醜い企みを打ち砕き　奴隷たちを解放する
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There the owner of the fortress, Hodir, trying to fool his vile intrigues and Arslan freed slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:10.28,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし　奴隷らは逆上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But slaves were furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:14.37,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,根深い人間の性を知り　困惑するのであった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When he learned that people are accustomed to such a system, he was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kashan castle
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:18.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン　ナルサス　その他　殿下のおそばにあって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Daryun, Narsus and your other wards,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The owner of the fortress of Kashan, Hodir
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,able to harm you ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:22.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下の害となる者どもを　これから排除いたします
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.23,0:16:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we get rid of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, do you advise me to quit Narsusa and Daryuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:27.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり　お主は私にナルサスやダリューンを捨てろというのだな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:28.97,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いかにも
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:35.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,では聞くが　ダリューンやナルサスを私が捨てて　お主を選んだとして
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Suppose I leave Daryuna and Narsusa, will choose you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:39.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,今度はお主を捨てる日が来ないと　なぜ言い切れる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the guarantee that one day you, too, as I did not give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You have told so much about Narsuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:42.37,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ナルサスの悪口をお主は言い立てる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:44.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど　ナルサスは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when he gave me shelter for the night
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:48.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私に一夜の宿を与えておいて　だまし討ちなどしなかったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and never secretly did not attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand before the angel of justice
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:58.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,問罪天使の前にまかり出て　生前の罪を告白するがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and confess their sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:03.57,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,自分は裏切ってはならぬものを　全て裏切りましたとな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:17:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Admit it, how dare you betray it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that he should not betray!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mark, go. Now you are free.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:13.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ　行くがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:16.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お前たちはもう自由なのだから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:19.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ホディール様がそうおっしゃったのですか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So said Mr. Hodir?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:22.97,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ホディールは死んだ　だから…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodir dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:25.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたが殺したのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:27.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私の仲間が…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,One of my friends ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.51,0:17:28.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.53,0:17:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:30.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ご主人様の敵だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Avenge the host!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:31.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私は…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,End!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:37.25,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.48,0:17:39.12,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:39.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,待て
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:48.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ナルサス　お主はこうなることが分かっていたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Narsus, you know what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:49.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:52.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ教えてくれなかったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was not I told?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:57.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,先にそう申し上げても　殿下は納得なさらなかったでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I had warned,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be unlikely to convince you it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:18:02.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,世の中　経験せねば分からないこともあると思いましたので
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:18:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that in the world some things are better to learn from their own experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:05.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それはお主自身のことなのか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:06.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:13.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,５年前　亡くなった父の跡を継いだとき　私は奴隷を解放しました
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years ago, when I inherited all after his father,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the freed slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:16.57,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,その後　王都に移っていたのですが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I went to the capital,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:19.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,しばらくして　故郷に戻りますと
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but when he came back,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:22.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,奴隷たちが舞い戻っていたのです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,servants reappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:23.97,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:30.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,寛大な主人の下に奴隷であることは　ある意味　最も楽な生き方なのです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just being a slave to some wealthy owner easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:35.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど　お主は信念に基づいて正義を行ったのではないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But you did it, because he thought it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:40.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,正義とは太陽ではなく　星のようなものかもしれません
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the best is considered not the sun and the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:46.25,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,星は天空に限りなくありますし　互いに光を打ち消し合います
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.27,0:18:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky infinite number of stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and they interrupt each other shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince, in any case, do not let my words completely seize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:53.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下　なんにしても　私の申し上げることに左右なされますな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:57.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下は大道を歩もうとしておられる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You are trying to go in the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:19:00.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ぜひ　その道をお進みください
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.37,0:19:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:06.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この頼もしい５人が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,These people are trustworthy ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:09.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いつまでこうやって　自分についてきてくれるのだろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How far they will go with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:13.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,彼らが愛想を尽かさないうちに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be worthy of the ruler as long as they are not disappointed in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:16.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,自分は立派な君主にならなければならない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:23.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それで　夜が明けましたら　いずれの方角へおいでになりますか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, soon the dawn where we are headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.98,0:19:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To the East. By fortress Peshavard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:24.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,東へ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:27.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ペシャワールへ向かう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, do not get stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:32.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,手を出すな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He killed my father and friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:35.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつはおやじと仲間の敵だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Arslan group had to split up because of the chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:39.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,追撃で分断されたアルスラーン一行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:45.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,その渦中　ナルサスはゾット族の娘　アルフリードを救出する
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Drawn into the fight, Narsus saves the Alfred, the leader of the clan daughter Zot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Daughter of Commander Zot clan, the Alfred
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Royal capital of Ecbatana
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kashan castle
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Peshavard
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:51.37,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,その後　数々の包囲網をくぐり抜け　合流を果たした一行は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,After avoiding the countless attempts to surround them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,group merged
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:57.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルス最大の戦力を残す東の拠点　ペシャワール城にたどり着いた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and finally arrived in the strongest fortress in the east, Peshavard,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,which he remained most of the Parsis forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:19:59.28,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王太子殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.14,0:20:01.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,バフマン
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Avalanches!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.02,0:20:04.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おお　よくぞ　ご無事で
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.04,0:20:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to see that you are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.08,0:20:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain of Cavalry of the kingdom Pars, Kisvard
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.08,0:20:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain of Cavalry of the kingdom Pars, Bahman
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:07.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,世話になるぞ　バフマン　キシュワード
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to stop you, Bachmann, Kisvard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:11.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルスはこのペシャワールから　反撃ののろしを上げる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Pars will fight back from here in Peshawar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:13.23,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなの力を貸してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So I ask for your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:13.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:19.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ペシャワール城にある騎馬２万　歩兵６万挙げて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.34,0:20:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty thousand horsemen and sixty thousand foot of the fortress of Peshawar
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:22.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下に忠誠を誓わせていただきますぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,will be honored for the privilege to serve you, Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:24.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,知らねばよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I'd never known.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This burden is not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.34,0:20:26.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,知るべきではなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:30.25,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,もし何もかも知らずにいられたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were possible to remain in ignorance,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have sworn eternal fidelity
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:35.37,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの聡明そうな王子に永遠の忠誠を誓うことができたであろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.28,0:20:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,this prince, who seems wise and prudent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:37.25,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いま一度　問う
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask again! Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:39.25,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お主は何者だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the son Osroesa, the previous king.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:46.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は先王オスロエスの子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:48.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ヒルメス
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.44,0:20:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hermes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:55.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-1.5}ペシャワール城に潜入した銀仮面卿ことヒルメスは　アルスラーンの命を狙う
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Peshavard penetrated into the fortress,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Silver mask, known as Hermes, attacked Arslan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:21:02.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,彼を救ったのはアルスラーン出生の秘密を知るバフマンであった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.35,0:21:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And his defense stood Bachmann, who knew the secret of the birth of Arslan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:06.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,バフマンか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Avalanches ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:12.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お懐かしゅうございます　ヒルメス殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Prince Hermes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:15.67,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ邪魔をした
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you prevented ?!
